-  a=pascalc\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309187\n", "files": ["security/manager/ssl/StaticHPKPins.h", "security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.inc"], "git_node": "191c6b23b37b9fcc5f16b51fc411de5ef2a19434", "git_parents": ["42ec8123546dcda3d87b881da0ceaef0a3865d1e"], "node": "d3d579b124b28b0cdd0fa3f1097775affbf6e2a7", "parents": ["90381ac6c689d08e786f412f5cb7a7b2f51e952f"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782567457, "git_changesets": ["191c6b23b37b9fcc5f16b51fc411de5ef2a19434"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27131": {"changesets": [{"author": "Release Engineering Landoscript \u003crelease+landoscript@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug - Import translations from main\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/app-links/src/main/res/values-sl/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/customtabs/src/main/res/values-bqi/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/prompts/src/main/res/values-kk/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/prompts/src/main/res/values-sl/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-bqi/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-it/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-pt-rBR/strings.xml", "mobile/android/focus-android/app/src/main/res/values-it/strings.xml"], "git_node": "0a69194bb22bb0f37e088d181b4409c0f6b7c07a", "git_parents": ["191c6b23b37b9fcc5f16b51fc411de5ef2a19434"], "node": "21372edb3870c828e9d3c78cfad474d095673bf0", "parents": ["d3d579b124b28b0cdd0fa3f1097775affbf6e2a7"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782612862, "git_changesets": ["0a69194bb22bb0f37e088d181b4409c0f6b7c07a"], "user": "ffxbld@lando.moz.tools"}, "27132": {"changesets": [{"author": "Gela \u003cgmalekpour@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2050463 - Correctly dispatch onboarding_not_now_tapped when user taps on Not now in onboarding sheet  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308795\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308870\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ipprotection/ui/IPProtectionBottomSheet.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ipprotection/ui/IPProtectionBottomSheetFragment.kt"], "git_node": "64371d90be15ede9e8c90f152ac86c609d07cb63", "git_parents": ["0a69194bb22bb0f37e088d181b4409c0f6b7c07a"], "node": "dfbc95ea8dcb547be10ae7f6b2a2466ab7a3d966", "parents": ["21372edb3870c828e9d3c78cfad474d095673bf0"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782631703, "git_changesets": ["64371d90be15ede9e8c90f152ac86c609d07cb63"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27133": {"changesets": [{"author": "Sajid Anwar \u003csajidanwar94@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2050458 - Restrict alignment-baseline synthesis to atomic inlines.  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308969\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309227\n", "files": ["layout/base/Baseline.cpp", "layout/generic/nsIFrame.cpp", "layout/generic/nsIFrame.h", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-inline/alignment-baseline/alignment-baseline-flex-item-export-001-ref.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-inline/alignment-baseline/alignment-baseline-flex-item-export-001.html"], "git_node": "42d52eb2feb88e52b44f1f3d54aa4c841626ea8a", "git_parents": ["64371d90be15ede9e8c90f152ac86c609d07cb63"], "node": "1045f00d4ecd12dedd84db0bb9de260c074c8234", "parents": ["dfbc95ea8dcb547be10ae7f6b2a2466ab7a3d966"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782631737, "git_changesets": ["42d52eb2feb88e52b44f1f3d54aa4c841626ea8a"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27134": {"changesets": [{"author": "sarah541 \u003csarahkhan1107@hotmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2050146 - Expose Search Optimization Feature secret settings on Beta  a=pascalc\n\nThe Secret Settings entry for the Search Optimization Feature was only\nvisible on Nightly and Debug builds. Make it visible on Beta as well so\nthe suggestion cards can be exercised there, while keeping it hidden on\nRelease.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308573\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309129\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/settings/SecretSettingsFragment.kt"], "git_node": "593696a2696a6d4d491e5955a9e15f0fdb82a885", "git_parents": ["42d52eb2feb88e52b44f1f3d54aa4c841626ea8a"], "node": "b8f7c078f845a04935cdf87e2649b270741fffc5", "parents": ["1045f00d4ecd12dedd84db0bb9de260c074c8234"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782631823, "git_changesets": ["593696a2696a6d4d491e5955a9e15f0fdb82a885"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27135": {"changesets": [{"author": "sarah541 \u003csarahkhan1107@hotmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2050103 - Show flight suggestion times in the airport's local timezone  a=pascalc\n\nThe FlightAware API returns arrival/departure times already in the\norigin/destination airport's local timezone, with the UTC offset baked\ninto the ISO string. parseFlightData re-projected those instants onto\nthe device's timezone, so a flight arriving at an airport ahead of the\nuser's zone displayed the wrong (earlier) time and could land on the\nwrong date.\n\nParse flight times while preserving the offset embedded in the string so\nthe card shows the airport-local wall-clock time.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308562\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309128\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/awesomebar/src/main/java/mozilla/components/feature/awesomebar/provider/FlightsOnlineSuggestionProvider.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/awesomebar/src/main/java/mozilla/components/feature/awesomebar/provider/ProviderUtils.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/awesomebar/src/test/java/mozilla/components/feature/awesomebar/provider/FlightsOnlineSuggestionProviderTest.kt"], "git_node": "79427794fff2417f1e96c5cf264b7915d78decb1", "git_parents": ["593696a2696a6d4d491e5955a9e15f0fdb82a885"], "node": "6b357e660f55f98b4e181eba8115154d17901917", "parents": ["b8f7c078f845a04935cdf87e2649b270741fffc5"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782631869, "git_changesets": ["79427794fff2417f1e96c5cf264b7915d78decb1"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27136": {"changesets": [{"author": "sarah541 \u003csarahkhan1107@hotmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2050095 - Query stock suggestions for any non-blank search  a=pascalc\n\nThe stocks provider only fetched suggestions when the query contained the\nliteral word \"stock\", so searching with the cashtag syntax (e.g. \"$AMZN\")\nor any other phrasing never produced a result card.\n\nForward whatever the user typed to the Merino endpoint and display a card\nonly when the API returns data, matching the flights provider's behavior.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308567\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309127\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/awesomebar/src/main/java/mozilla/components/feature/awesomebar/provider/StocksOnlineSuggestionProvider.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/awesomebar/src/test/java/mozilla/components/feature/awesomebar/provider/StocksOnlineSuggestionProviderTest.kt"], "git_node": "560c247e2df507480742b93046314d32e5320752", "git_parents": ["79427794fff2417f1e96c5cf264b7915d78decb1"], "node": "cf151ab04d31ea0e7d62b672aff7d96423c0b190", "parents": ["6b357e660f55f98b4e181eba8115154d17901917"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782631905, "git_changesets": ["560c247e2df507480742b93046314d32e5320752"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27137": {"changesets": [{"author": "Lee Salzman \u003clsalzman@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2049805.  a=pascalc\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308860\n", "files": ["gfx/layers/wr/WebRenderMessageUtils.h", "gfx/webrender_bindings/WebRenderTypes.h"], "git_node": "1ce436e2a10d59f18844073c2997ff0e66631e98", "git_parents": ["560c247e2df507480742b93046314d32e5320752"], "node": "bca82bc5b4c68b24fe2e922876a3f39b9dc4cad7", "parents": ["cf151ab04d31ea0e7d62b672aff7d96423c0b190"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782632048, "git_changesets": ["1ce436e2a10d59f18844073c2997ff0e66631e98"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27138": {"changesets": [{"author": "giorga \u003cgiorga@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2049602 - Fix Crash [@ android.os.FileUriExposedException: at android.os.StrictMode.onFileUriExposed(StrictMode.java)] at DownloadUIShareMiddleware.  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308228\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309045\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/support/utils/src/main/java/mozilla/components/support/utils/DefaultDownloadFileUtils.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/support/utils/src/main/java/mozilla/components/support/utils/DownloadFileUtils.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/support/utils/src/test/java/mozilla/components/support/utils/DefaultDownloadFileUtilsTest.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/support/utils/src/testFixtures/kotlin/mozilla/components/support/utils/FakeDownloadFileUtils.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/downloads/listscreen/middleware/DownloadUIShareMiddleware.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/downloads/listscreen/middleware/DownloadUIShareMiddlewareTest.kt"], "git_node": "76991cf5ecf4b989de8da4f645267ab7128b15fc", "git_parents": ["1ce436e2a10d59f18844073c2997ff0e66631e98"], "node": "8be545d73a4fc5288543d30cc78b38350a503fbf", "parents": ["bca82bc5b4c68b24fe2e922876a3f39b9dc4