ttps://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308081\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308924\n", "files": ["browser/extensions/formautofill/test/unit/test_paymentsListItems.js", "browser/extensions/formautofill/test/unit/xpcshell.toml", "toolkit/components/formautofill/FormAutofillPreferences.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "27e5a7d25e5655a71316ff0bac38147927ce535e", "git_parents": ["e565a31e8c0a07e0fa2d730918f1402fe291ed3d"], "node": "bf6d7f3f2e6d626f8908edd4e6e14e8679136e99", "parents": ["21c9140213ab84d261bc909d1e7b86df1602afd7"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782632349, "git_changesets": ["27e5a7d25e5655a71316ff0bac38147927ce535e"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27143": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jamie Nicol \u003cjnicol@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2048345 - Make RemoteSurfaceAllocator ensure that surfaces are owned by the calling client.  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308282\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308986\n", "files": ["mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/aidl/org/mozilla/gecko/process/IChildProcess.aidl", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/aidl/org/mozilla/gecko/process/IProcessManager.aidl", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/gfx/RemoteSurfaceAllocator.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/gfx/SurfaceAllocator.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/process/GeckoProcessManager.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/process/GeckoServiceChildProcess.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/process/GeckoServiceGpuProcess.java"], "git_node": "3c0ff02ed258f2857783b642e0556b25e47b0b99", "git_parents": ["27e5a7d25e5655a71316ff0bac38147927ce535e"], "node": "16eff318e511332bcec5f597f23a0792ad1fd021", "parents": ["bf6d7f3f2e6d626f8908edd4e6e14e8679136e99"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782632384, "git_changesets": ["3c0ff02ed258f2857783b642e0556b25e47b0b99"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27144": {"changesets": [{"author": "Naz\u0131m Can Alt\u0131nova \u003ccanaltinova@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2047859 - Read LUL unwind info for libraries loaded from inside the APK on Android  a=pascalc\n\nAfter legacy packaging was disabled (bug 1867280), native libraries like\nlibxul.so are loaded directly from inside the APK/AAB instead of being\nextracted uncompressed to disk. The dynamic linker reports their path\nusing the \"\u003capk\u003e!/\u003centry\u003e\" syntax (for example:\n\".../split_config.arm64_v8a.apk!/lib/ arm64-v8a/libxul.so\"), which is\nnot a real filesystem path.\n\nBug 1773313 already moved breakpadId/codeId extraction to read from\nmemory, so that metadata was correct. But LUL still obtained unwinding\ninformation by `open()`ing the library file from disk. With the\n\"\u003capk\u003e!/\" path, that `open()` fails, and because of that,\n`NotifyAfterMap()` never gets called for libxul and libmozglue, and\nstack walking gets broken due to this.\n\nThe library is stored uncompressed and page-aligned inside the APK, so\nit can still be mapped by opening the APK and mapping at the library's\noffset within it. It is the file offset of the mapping that backs the\nlibrary's first loaded page, which we recover from /proc/self/maps.\n\nIf the offset can't be resolved we fall back to NotifyExecutableArea()\nso that stack scanning still works.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D307383\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308909\n", "files": ["tools/profiler/lul/AutoObjectMapper.cpp", "tools/profiler/lul/AutoObjectMapper.h", "tools/profiler/lul/platform-linux-lul.cpp"], "git_node": "458e8ad2106ac5bc02277ef0e0098bd4dbda1abb", "git_parents": ["3c0ff02ed258f2857783b642e0556b25e47b0b99"], "node": "212e442b50168d54aee910b59203bfe393a02601", "parents": ["16eff318e511332bcec5f597f23a0792ad1fd021"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782632423, "git_changesets": ["458e8ad2106ac5bc02277ef0e0098bd4dbda1abb"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27145": {"changesets": [{"author": "lottiehope \u003clottie_hope@hotmail.co.uk\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2046129 - Only show the Change wallpaper menu item when on the Homepage  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308036\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308821\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/efficiency/selectors/MainMenuSelectors.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/components/menu/compose/MainMenu.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/components/menu/compose/MainMenuTest.kt"], "git_node": "c5c75f4100fb66cd405a28f7ded3c949c8fbd2ad", "git_parents": ["458e8ad2106ac5bc02277ef0e0098bd4dbda1abb"], "node": "fb2026a0745e537d07a8ee3514fd8dab86cbb3b9", "parents": ["212e442b50168d54aee910b59203bfe393a02601"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782632483, "git_changesets": ["c5c75f4100fb66cd405a28f7ded3c949c8fbd2ad"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27146": {"changesets": [{"author": "Brad Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2045626: Compute range of convolve filter in integer domain.  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308096\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D309194\n", "files": ["gfx/2d/SkConvolver.cpp"], "git_node": "2f3289e5d6dc7ac3faa5e17c52d638ba5e89bb59", "git_parents": ["c5c75f4100fb66cd405a28f7ded3c949c8fbd2ad"], "node": "37cadad05725cbd741a4d122991d8f05d075a9a8", "parents": ["fb2026a0745e537d07a8ee3514fd8dab86cbb3b9"], "tags": []}], "date": 1782632675, "git_changesets": ["2f3289e5d6dc7ac3faa5e17c52d638ba5e89bb59"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "27147": {"changesets": [{"author": "Alastor Wu \u003calwu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2